==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: guǎnzi
===Etymology===
From [[管]] (a cylindrical double reed woodwind instrument made of wood; literally "pipe" or "tube") + [[子]] (a suffix).

===Noun===
'''[[管]][[子]]'''

# a cylindrical double reed woodwind instrument made of hardwood (originally bamboo) and used primarily in northern China. 

===Synonyms===
*[[管]]

